2019 was a very special year. I had the honor of meeting and photographing incredible individuals with inspiring stories. I also had the privilege of being the guest editor of HUMANITY @citizensofhumanity where I was also interviewing the subjects as well as capturing their portraits.
Thank you so much to all the people that made it possible! ❤️❤️❤️

What an honor to be selected as one of @time “best portrait of 2019”. And thank you @lizzobeeating for your trust and energy to make this image come to live. Sometimes as a photographer we have an image in our minds, but everything can change when you meet the talent and all the elements come together on set. Sometimes, like in this case, everything perfectly aligned and the image just happened on frame 16th of the first look.
